{"data":[{"id":"1708407645172459","contents":"# JSON 기반의 메타 데이터 관리  소개 \n- Tag 테이블에 대한 METADATA 필드에 JSON 기반으로 다양한 계층 구조 관리 가능 \n\n## 바이너리 데모 스키마 \n\n```sql\nCREATE TAG TABLE iiot_tag (    \n  name  VARCHAR(32) PRIMARY KEY,\n  time  DATETIME BASETIME,    \n  value JSON SUMMARIZED)\nMETADATA (asset   JSON INDEX('customer.id', 'site.id', 'line.id', 'equipment.type', 'sensor.slot', 'criticality'),\n          profile JSON INDEX('sampling.hz', 'zone', 'priority')) ;\n\n```\n## 데이터 샘플 입력\n\n```sql\nINSERT INTO iiot_tag METADATA VALUES \n(\n'EQ02_S04’, \n'{\"customer\":{\"id\":\"CUST_A\"}, \"site\":{\"id\":\"SITE_1\"}, \"line\":{\"id\":\"LINE_2\"}, \"equipment\":{\"type\":\"PUMP\"},\n  \"sensor\":{\"slot\":\"S04\"}, \"criticality\":\"HIGH\"}’, \n'{\"sampling\":{\"hz\":1234},\"zone\":\"KOR\", \"priority\":\"VERY HIGH\"}’\n);\n\nSELECT name,\n        asset->'$.site.id' AS site_id,\n        asset->'$.line.id' AS line_id, \n        asset->'$.equipment.type' AS equipment_type, \n        profile->'$.zone' AS zone, \n        asset->'$.criticality' AS criticality  FROM iiot_tag METADATA \nWHERE profile->’$.zone’ = ‘KOR’ \n      and \n      asset->’$.line.id’=22\nORDER BY name;\n\n```\n## 메타 데이터 JSON 수정 함수\n```sql\nJSON_SET(col, jsonpath, value) : 특정 값을 갱신\nJSON_REMOVE(col, jsonpath) : 특정 값을 제거 \nJSON_SET_JSON(col, jsonpath_key, value) : JSON key:value 구조를 추가 \n```\n\n```sql\n갱신\nUPDATE iiot_tag METADATA SET profile = json_set(profile, '$.priority', 'HIGH')  WHERE name = 'EQ02_S04';\n추가\nUPDATE iiot_tag METADATA SET profile = json_set_json(profile, '$.sampling', '{\"hz\":10}')  WHERE name = 'EQ02_S04’;\n제거\nUPDATE iiot_tag METADATA set profile = json_set_remove(profile, '$.zone') where asset->'$.equipment.type' = 'PUMP’;\n```\n","height":805,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true}]}